</disciplines><abstract>&lt;p&gt;This brief provides a summary of the Anti-Assignment Clause of the Social Security Act and administrative offsets. It provides a description of the child support offset, food stamp dept offset, student loan offset, and interim assistance recoupment. It concludes with a discussion of implications for BPA&amp;O and PABSS programs.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
